org.wildfly.swarm.config.logging

Class AsyncHandler<T extends AsyncHandler<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.swarm.config.logging.AsyncHandler<T>

  • public class AsyncHandler<T extends AsyncHandler<T>>
extends Object
    Defines a handler which writes to the sub-handlers in an asynchronous thread. Used for handlers which introduce a substantial amount of lag.
